tracks.title: Harvest Moon
tracks.description:
This is a Neil Young cover. We wanted to give out some new music while we are finishing up our album. We thought a cover would be a good idea and since we both love Harvest Moon we decided to give it a try. It's super intimidating to cover Neil Young so we tried to make it a lot different, just so we didn't have to "compete" with the master.
Thanks to Coco Morier for the beautiful backing vocals and Dan "Cosmic Kids" Terndrup for his incredible finger snaps!

tracks.title: Pierce The Veil - Bulls In The Bronx
tracks.description:
Download Pierce The Veil's new song "Bulls In The Bronx", now available on iTunes. 

The track is taken from the bands new album 'Collide The Sky' that is available now

ITUNES: http://smarturl.it/CollideWithTheSky

EU CD & MERCH PRE-ORDER: http://piercetheveil.firebrandstore.com/
US CD & MERCH PRE-ORDER: http://piercetheveil.merchnow.com/

PIERCE THE VEIL - Vic Fuentes (Vocals), Mike Fuentes (Drums), Tony Perry (Guitar), Jaime Preciado (Bass) - With a unique brand of progressive post-hardcore, Pierce The Veil have captured a rabid fan base across the globe. Deploying every shred of musical prowess in their artillery, Pierce The Veil are anxiously awaiting the release of their much anticipated new album Collide With The Sky. Gaining a reputation for their explosive live show and the unique vocal style of singer Vic Fuentes, the band has gained press support from Alternative Press, AMP, Outburn, Kerrang!, IGN, Revolver, AOL, And FUSE TV. Primed with an incredible new album and a rigorous tour schedule, Pierce The Veil are truly en fuego this summer!
